<script type="text/javascript">
var CSMReqs={af:{c:2,p:'atf'},cf:{c:2,p:'cf'}};
var DPTimestamps={mainImgRepl:{c:1}};
var prioritizeCriticalModules = true;
var setCSMReq = function(a){
    a=a.toLowerCase();
    var b=CSMReqs[a];

    if(--b.c==0){
        if(typeof b.f == 'function'){
            b.f();
        }
        else{
            if(typeof uet=='function'){uet(a);};

        if (a == 'af' && prioritizeCriticalModules){
            var featureElements = document.getElementsByClassName('dp-cif');
            if(featureElements.length){
                var priorityModuleList = ["A","jQuery"];
                var moduleMap = {
                    'A' : 1,
                    'jQuery' : 1
                };
                for (var i = 0; i<featureElements.length; i++){
                    if(featureElements[i].dataset && featureElements[i].dataset.dpCriticalJsModules){
                        var criticalJsModules = JSON.parse(featureElements[i].dataset.dpCriticalJsModules);
                        if(criticalJsModules) {
                            criticalJsModules.forEach(function(criticalJsModule,index){
                                if (!moduleMap[criticalJsModule]){
                                    moduleMap[criticalJsModule] = 1;
                                    priorityModuleList.push(criticalJsModule);
                                }
                            });
                        }
                    } else if (typeof featureElements[i].dataset === 'undefined'){
                        var criticalJsModules = JSON.parse(featureElements[i].getAttribute('data-dp-critical-js-modules'));
                        if(criticalJsModules) {
                            criticalJsModules.forEach(function(criticalJsModule,index){
                                if (!moduleMap[criticalJsModule]){
                                    moduleMap[criticalJsModule] = 1;
                                    priorityModuleList.push(criticalJsModule);
                                }
                            }); 
                        }   
                    }
                }

                if (P && P.setPriority && typeof P.setPriority === 'function' ) {
                    prioritizeCriticalModules = false;
                    P.setPriority(priorityModuleList);
                }
            }
        }
            if(typeof P != 'undefined'){
                P.register(b.p);
            };
        }
    }
}

var setDPTimestamp = function(a, t){
    var b=DPTimestamps[a];
    var w = window;
    if(b && --b.c===0){
        if (w.ue && typeof w.ue_t0 !== 'undefined' && typeof w.ue.count==='function') {
            w.ue.count(a, Date.now()-w.ue_t0);
            if(t && w.ue && w.ue.tag) {w.ue.tag(t);}
        }
    }
}

var addlongPoleTag = function(marker,customtag){
    marker=marker.toLowerCase();
    var b=CSMReqs[marker];
    if(b.c==0){
        if(window.ue && ue.tag) {ue.tag(customtag);}
    }
}


</script>

<script type="text/javascript">
  if(window.navmet===undefined) {
    window.navmet=[];
    if (window.performance && window.performance.timing && window.ue_t0) {
      var t = window.performance.timing;
      var now = + new Date();
      window.navmet.basic = {
        'networkLatency': (t.responseStart - t.fetchStart),
        'navFirstPaint': (now - t.responseStart),
        'NavStart': (now - window.ue_t0)
      };
      window.navmet.push({key:"NavFirstPaintStart",end:+new Date(),begin:window.ue_t0});
    }
  }
  if (window.ue_t0) {
     window.navmet.push({key:"NavMainStart",end:+new Date(),begin:window.ue_t0});
  }
</script>

<script>
window.logIfVideoSizeDiffCalled = false;
window.logIfVideoSizeDiff = function(containerHeight) {
try {
if (window.logIfVideoSizeDiffCalled) {
return;
}
window.logIfVideoSizeDiffCalled = true;
var videoWrapperHeight = ((document.getElementsByClassName('video-wrapper')[0]||{}).clientHeight||containerHeight);
var videoWrapperDifference = videoWrapperHeight - containerHeight;
if (videoWrapperDifference > 1) {
if (window.ue) {
window.ue.count("imageBlock-mobile-videoSizeDiff", 1);
}
if (window.ueLogError) {
var customError = { message: '[ImageBlock Video Size Diff: Video is larger than image-block; ASIN:B09H3N5J27' };
var additionalInfo = {
logLevel: 'WARN',
attribution: 'imageBlock-mobile-videoSizeDiff'
};
window.ueLogError(customError, additionalInfo);
}
return true;
}
} catch (err) {
P.log('Fatal occurred in AibScript', 'FATAL', 'DetailPageMediaBlockTemplates');
}
return false;
}
var finalAltImageSizes = [[900, 900], [900, 900], [900, 900], [900, 900], [900, 900], [1017, 900], [900, 900], [900, 900], [900, 900]];
var lastMainImageDims = lastMainImageDims === undefined ? finalAltImageSizes[0].slice() : lastMainImageDims;
var isAibScriptExecuted = false, aibImageWrappers, aibContainerHeight;
var aibMaxHeight = 450;
var aibMinHeight = 450;
function viewportDimension() {
var e = window,
a = 'inner';
if (!('innerWidth' in window)) {
a = 'client';
e = document.documentElement || document.body;
}
return {
width: e[a + 'Width'],
height: e[a + 'Height']
};
}
function getNewImgAndContDims(imgWidth, imgHeight, origHeight) {
var viewPortWidth = viewportDimension().width - 20;
var maxHeight = aibMaxHeight, minHeight = aibMinHeight;
var imageWrappers = document.querySelectorAll('.image-size-wrapper');
var index = imageWrappers.length-1;
while(index >=0 && imageWrappers[index].querySelector('.slate-image-table') != null) {
minHeight = Math.max(minHeight, imageWrappers[index].getAttribute("data-image-height"));
index--;
}
var newMainImageHeight = (imgHeight * viewPortWidth)/imgWidth;
newMainImageHeight = Math.min(Math.min(newMainImageHeight, origHeight), maxHeight);
var containerHeight = Math.min(Math.max(newMainImageHeight, minHeight), maxHeight);
return {
image: newMainImageHeight,
container: containerHeight
};
}
function aibEnlargeIB(d) {
if(!isAibScriptExecuted) {
try {
var scriptStartTime = Date.now(), scriptEndTime;
var landingImg = d.getElementById("main-image");
var mainImageHeight = landingImg.naturalHeight, mainImageWidth = landingImg.naturalWidth;
if (mainImageHeight == 1 && mainImageWidth == 1) {
return;
}
lastMainImageDims[0] = mainImageWidth;
lastMainImageDims[1] = mainImageHeight;
var newDims = getNewImgAndContDims(mainImageWidth, mainImageHeight, finalAltImageSizes[0][1]);
var newMainImageHeight = newDims.image;
aibContainerHeight = newDims.container;
aibImageWrappers = d.getElementById("image-block").querySelectorAll('.image-size-wrapper');
landingImg.style.height = newMainImageHeight+'px';
landingImg.style.width = ((mainImageWidth * newMainImageHeight)/mainImageHeight)+'px';
for (var i=0, len=aibImageWrappers.length; i< len; i++) {
if (!aibImageWrappers[i].classList.contains("aib-video-wrapper")) {
// Fix for https://sim.amazon.com/issues/SLDP-1979, as this causes
// an issue when the main images are small and video is wide
var height = aibContainerHeight;
var sitbStickerContainer = aibImageWrappers[i].querySelector("#sitb-sticker-container-inner") || aibImageWrappers[i].querySelector("#sitb-sticker-container");
if (sitbStickerContainer) {
height += sitbStickerContainer.clientHeight;
}
aibImageWrappers[i].style.height = height+'px';
}
}
var videoTable = d.getElementsByClassName("video-table");
for(var i=0, len=videoTable.length; i<len; i++) {
videoTable[i].style.height = aibContainerHeight+'px';
}
isAibScriptExecuted = true;
scriptEndTime = Date.now();
if (window.ue) {
window.ue.count("dp_aib_mob_js_exec_time", scriptEndTime-scriptStartTime);
}
if (window.logIfVideoSizeDiff) {
window.logIfVideoSizeDiff(aibContainerHeight);
}
} catch (err) {
var metricName = "aib_exp2_jsFailed";
var ue = window.ue;
if (ue) {
var existingValue = ue.count(metricName) || 0;
ue.count(metricName, existingValue + 1);
}
if (window.ueLogError) {
var jsError = {
logLevel: "ERROR",
attribution: "DetailPageAibJs",
message: "[DP][AIB][Exp2] JS Execution failed: " + JSON.stringify(err)
};
window.ueLogError(jsError);
}
} finally {
d.getElementById("main-image").style.visibility = "visible";
}
}
}
</script>

if (typeof window.markFeatureRender === 'function') {

window.markFeatureRender('imageBlock',options);
}
});

<script type="text/javascript">
(function(d,w){
var url = "https://m.media-amazon.com/images/I/71bFD4OHJiL._AC_UY900_.jpg";
var i = new Image();
i.onload = function () {
var img = d.getElementById("main-image");
if (img) {
img.src = url;
var imgWidth = img.width;
var imgHeight = img.height;
var hiResWidth = img.naturalWidth;
var hiResHeight = img.naturalHeight;
try {
var hiResHeightGood = (imgWidth / hiResWidth) * hiResHeight;
var heightDistortion = (Math.abs(hiResHeightGood - imgHeight) / imgHeight).toFixed(2);
if (heightDistortion > .01) {
if (window.ue) {
window.ue.count("imageBlock-mobile-hi_res", 1);
}
if (window.ueLogError) {
var customError = { message: '[ImageBlock Hi-Res: Size distortion. ASIN:B09H3N5J27 Diff:' + heightDistortion.toString() + ']' };
var additionalInfo = {
logLevel: 'WARN',
attribution: 'imageBlock-mobile-hi_res'
};
window.ueLogError(customError, additionalInfo);
}
}
}
catch (e) {
if (window.ueLogError) {
var additionalInfo = {
logLevel: 'WARN',
attribution: 'imageBlock-mobile-hi_res'
};
window.ueLogError(e, additionalInfo);
}
}
}
w.setDPTimestamp("mainImgRepl", img ? "inlineScript2" : "mainImgNotFound");
}
i.src = url;
})(document,window);

P.when('jQuery').register('airy-image-block', function($) {
var shouldDetachExitFullScreen = false;
var currentIndex = 0;
var currentVideoIndex = 0;
var curContext;
var videoIndexPlayedPV = {};
var videoIndexPlayedIV = {};
var newAiryConfig = null;
var updateStateElement = $('#image-block');
return {
updateStateForAction : function($carousel, index, airyConfig) {
if (!airyConfig) {return;}
var airyInstance = airyConfig.instance;
if (airyInstance) {
airyInstance.pause();
}
currentVideoIndex = index;
curContext = airyConfig.contextName;
var $selectedCarouselItem = $carousel
.find('li.a-carousel-card')
.eq(index - 1);
var $playerContainer = $selectedCarouselItem.find('.airy-player-container');
if (!$playerContainer.length) {
return;
}
if (airyInstance) {
this._attachAndLoadMedia(airyInstance, $playerContainer);
return;
}
P.when('Airy').execute(function() {
airyInstance = this._embed($playerContainer, airyConfig.contextName);
airyConfig.embeddedCallback(airyInstance);
}.bind(this));
},
_embed : function($playerContainer, contextName) {
var $videoMetadata = $('#image-block-video-metadata');
var foresterParams = $videoMetadata.data('forester-params');
if (contextName != null) {
foresterParams.method += '.' + contextName;
}
var airyInstance;
var that = this;
var playerConfig = {
foresterMetadataParams : foresterParams,
mediaSourceInfo : $playerContainer.data('video-url'),
parentElement : $playerContainer[0],
bindings : {
screenchange : function() {
var airyConfig = that.getNewAiryConfig();
if(airyConfig) {
airyInstance = airyConfig.instance;
if(airyInstance && !airyInstance.isFullScreen() && that.shouldDetachOnExitFullScreen()) {
that.setShouldDetachOnExitFullScreen(false);
that._detachAiryInstance(airyInstance);
that.updateStateForAction(that.getUpdateStateElement(), that.getCurrentIndex(), that.getNewAiryConfig());
}
}
},
normalscreen : function() {
if(!airyInstance && airyConfig) {
airyInstance = airyConfig.instance;
}
},
play : function() {
var inImmersive = curContext === 'ImmersiveView';
var videoMap = inImmersive ? videoIndexPlayedIV : videoIndexPlayedPV;
var metric = inImmersive ? "dpmob_videoPlayedIV" : "dpmob_videoPlayedPV";
if (!videoMap[currentVideoIndex]) {
videoMap[currentVideoIndex] = true;
if(window.ue && ue.count) { ue.count(metric); }
}
airyInstance.enterFullScreen({isAsync : true});
},
uiready : function() {
}
},
installFlashButtonText : "Install Flash Player",
installFlashPrompt : "Adobe Flash Player is required to watch this video.",
playbackErrorPrompt : "Sorry, an error has occurred while attempting video playback. Please try again later.",
videoUnsupportedPrompt : "Sorry, this video is unsupported on this browser.",
ageGate : {
deniedPrompt : "We're sorry. You are not old enough to watch this video.",
monthNames : [
"January",
"February",
"March",
"April",
"May",
"June",
"July",
"August",
"September",
"October",
"November",
"December"
],
prompt : "This video is not intended for all audiences. What date were you born?",
submitText : "Submit",
regionCode : "na"
}
};
this._addSlateImageToPlayerConfig($playerContainer, playerConfig);
airyInstance = Airy.embed(playerConfig);
return airyInstance;
},
_attachAndLoadMedia : function(airyInstance, $playerContainer) {
if (!airyInstance) { return; }
airyInstance.attach($playerContainer[0]);
this._loadMedia(airyInstance, $playerContainer);
},
_loadMedia : function(airyInstance, $playerContainer) {
if (!airyInstance) { return; }
var videoUrl = $playerContainer.data('video-url');
if (airyInstance.getMediaSourceInfo() === videoUrl) { return; }
var loadMediaConfig = {
mediaSourceInfo : videoUrl
};
this._addSlateImageToPlayerConfig($playerContainer, loadMediaConfig);
airyInstance.loadMedia(loadMediaConfig);
},
_addSlateImageToPlayerConfig : function($playerContainer, playerConfig) {
var slateUrl = $playerContainer.data('slate-url');
var $slateImage = $playerContainer.find('.image-size-wrapper');
var slateUrlMatchesImageUrl = $slateImage.find('img').attr('src') === slateUrl;
var slateImageValue = slateUrlMatchesImageUrl ? $slateImage[0] : slateUrl;
playerConfig.slateImages = {
preloadSlate : slateImageValue
};
},
_detachAiryInstance : function(airyInstance) {
if (airyInstance && !airyInstance.isDetached() && !airyInstance.isFullScreen()) {
airyInstance.detach({isAsync : true});
}
},
setShouldDetachOnExitFullScreen : function(shouldDetach) {
shouldDetachExitFullScreen = shouldDetach;
},
shouldDetachOnExitFullScreen : function() {
return shouldDetachExitFullScreen;
},
_resizeIVCarousel : function() {
if($('#immersive-main img').length > 0){
var mainCarouselHeight = getMainCarouselHeight();
$('#immersive-main').css('height',mainCarouselHeight+'px');
$('#immersive-main ol').css('height',mainCarouselHeight+'px');
$('#immersive-main div.a-carousel-viewport').each(function(){
$(this).css('height',mainCarouselHeight+'px');
});
$('#immersive-main li.a-carousel-card').each(function(){
$(this).css('height',mainCarouselHeight+'px');
});
$('#immersive-main img').each(function(){
$(this).css('max-height',mainCarouselHeight+'px');
});
$('#immersive-main .slate-image-table img').each(function() {
$(this).css('max-height',(mainCarouselHeight - 65) + 'px');
});
}
},
getCurrentIndex : function() {
return currentIndex;
},
setCurrentIndex : function(index) {
currentIndex = index;
},
getNewAiryConfig : function() {
return newAiryConfig;
},
setNewAiryConfig : function(airyConfig) {
newAiryConfig = airyConfig
},
getUpdateStateElement : function() {
return updateStateElement;
},
setUpdateStateElement : function(element) {
updateStateElement = element;
},
imageBlockRefresh : function() {
videoIndexPlayedIV = {};
videoIndexPlayedPV = {};
}
};
});

P.register("sizeChartV2Data", function() {
var seenMetrics = new Set();
return {
hasMultipleSizeCharts: true,
hasError: false,
recordMetricOnce: function(name, val) {
if (seenMetrics.has(name)) {
return;
}
var ue = window.ue;
if (ue && ue.count) {
ue.count(name + ":Csm", val);
}
seenMetrics.add(name);
}
};
});
}));</script> <script type="text/javascript">(function(f) {var _np=(window.P._namespace("FitViewContainer"));if(_np.guardFatal){_np.guardFatal(f)(_np);}else{f(_np);}}(function(P) {

<div id="R2DUCLQOSLAL62" data-hook="mobley-review-content" class="a-section a-spacing-large aok-relative"><div data-hook="genome-widget" class="a-row"><a href="/gp/profile/amzn1.account.AEFQY3X3BH4C6GVV7LSB2QITUF7Q/ref=cm_cr_dp_mb_gw_tr?ie=UTF8" class="a-profile" data-a-size="small"><div aria-hidden="true" class="a-profile-avatar-wrapper"><div class="a-profile-avatar"><img src="https://images-na.ssl-images-amazon.com/images/G/01/x-locale/common/grey-pixel.gif" class="a-lazy-loaded" data-src="https://images-na.ssl-images-amazon.com/images/S/amazon-avatars-global/default._CR0,0,1024,1024_SX110_.png"><noscript><img src="https://images-na.ssl-images-amazon.com/images/S/amazon-avatars-global/default._CR0,0,1024,1024_SX110_.png"/></noscript></div></div><div class="a-profile-content"><span class="a-profile-name">Amazon Customer</span></div></a></div><div id="customer_review-R2DUCLQOSLAL62" class="a-section celwidget" data-csa-c-id="lexe5d-lw6v6z-sq8uyy-yv1cx7"><div class="a-row a-spacing-micro a-grid-vertical-align a-grid-center"><i data-hook="review-star-rating" class="a-icon a-icon-star-small a-star-small-5 review-rating aok-align-center"><span class="a-icon-alt">5.0 out of 5 stars</span></i><span class="a-letter-space"></span><span data-hook="msrp-avp-badge-linkless" class="a-size-mini a-color-state a-text-bold">Verified Purchase</span></div><span data-hook="review-title" class="a-size-base review-title-content a-color-base a-text-bold">
<span>Good shoe</span>
</span><div data-hook="review-by-line" class="a-row a-spacing-none reviewByLine"><span data-hook="review-date" class="a-size-small a-color-tertiary review-date">Reviewed in the United States on May 25, 2024</span></div><span class="cr-original-truncatable-content">
<div class="a-row a-spacing-small cr-truncated-content"><span data-hook="review-body" class="review-text-sub-contents">
I always buy the fresh foams since my last pair lasted a really long time. The laces on these are a little thin but that’s easy to replace and the soles I think can have a better grip pattern as the road paint can become slippery if wet with these. All that being said,...
</span><span class="a-letter-space"></span><span class="a-declarative" data-action="reviews:toggle-class:click" data-csa-c-type="widget" data-csa-c-func-deps="aui-da-reviews:toggle-class:click" data-reviews:toggle-class:click="{&quot;cssClass&quot;:&quot;aok-hidden&quot;,&quot;selector&quot;:&quot;#customer_review-R2DUCLQOSLAL62 .cr-truncated-content, #customer_review-R2DUCLQOSLAL62 .cr-full-content&quot;}"><a data-hook="redirect-see-more" aria-label="Toggle full review text" class="a-link-normal a-nowrap a-text-normal" href="/gp/aw/review/B09H3N5J27/R2DUCLQOSLAL62/ref=cm_cr_dp_mb_rvw_tr?ie=UTF8"><span class="a-size-base cr-read-more">See more</span></a></span></div><div class="a-row a-spacing-small cr-full-content aok-hidden"><span data-hook="review-body" class="review-text-sub-contents">
I always buy the fresh foams since my last pair lasted a really long time. The laces on these are a little thin but that’s easy to replace and the soles I think can have a better grip pattern as the road paint can become slippery if wet with these. All that being said, they’re comfortable, durable, and inexpensive. For the price I’ll keep buying this type of shoe
</span></div></span>

</span></div></div></div></div><div id="R33ST7BFC9JOA8" data-hook="mobley-review-content" class="a-section a-spacing-large aok-relative"><div data-hook="genome-widget" class="a-row"><a href="/gp/profile/amzn1.account.AF2G76IFIOIMAHTNOZCCDCPWOSFA/ref=cm_cr_dp_mb_gw_tr?ie=UTF8" class="a-profile" data-a-size="small"><div aria-hidden="true" class="a-profile-avatar-wrapper"><div class="a-profile-avatar"><img src="https://images-na.ssl-images-amazon.com/images/G/01/x-locale/common/grey-pixel.gif" class="a-lazy-loaded" data-src="https://images-na.ssl-images-amazon.com/images/S/amazon-avatars-global/default._CR0,0,1024,1024_SX110_.png"><noscript><img src="https://images-na.ssl-images-amazon.com/images/S/amazon-avatars-global/default._CR0,0,1024,1024_SX110_.png"/></noscript></div></div><div class="a-profile-content"><span class="a-profile-name">Jose Rodriguez</span></div></a></div><div id="customer_review-R33ST7BFC9JOA8" class="a-section celwidget" data-csa-c-id="xt558n-z0ktmy-axjelt-p3vtkl"><div class="a-row a-spacing-micro a-grid-vertical-align a-grid-center"><i data-hook="review-star-rating" class="a-icon a-icon-star-small a-star-small-5 review-rating aok-align-center"><span class="a-icon-alt">5.0 out of 5 stars</span></i><span class="a-letter-space"></span><span data-hook="msrp-avp-badge-linkless" class="a-size-mini a-color-state a-text-bold">Verified Purchase</span></div><span data-hook="review-title" class="a-size-base review-title-content a-color-base a-text-bold">
<span>Comfortable and great quality kicks</span>
</span><div data-hook="review-by-line" class="a-row a-spacing-none reviewByLine"><span data-hook="review-date" class="a-size-small a-color-tertiary review-date">Reviewed in the United States on November 25, 2023</span></div><div class="a-row a-spacing-mini a-grid-vertical-align a-grid-center"><span data-hook="format-strip-linkless" class="a-size-small a-color-tertiary">Size: 9.5<i class="a-icon a-icon-text-separator" role="img" aria-label="|"></i>Color: Black/Silver Metallic/Gum 2</span></div><span class="cr-original-truncatable-content">
<div class="a-row a-spacing-small cr-truncated-content"><span data-hook="review-body" class="review-text-sub-contents">
I recently purchased a pair of New Balance Men's Fresh Foam Arishi V4 Running shoes, and I couldn't be happier with my new kicks. These shoes have truly elevated my running experience to another level. First and foremost, the comfort and cushioning provided by...
</span><span class="a-letter-space"></span><span class="a-declarative" data-action="reviews:toggle-class:click" data-csa-c-type="widget" data-csa-c-func-deps="aui-da-reviews:toggle-class:click" data-reviews:toggle-class:click="{&quot;cssClass&quot;:&quot;aok-hidden&quot;,&quot;selector&quot;:&quot;#customer_review-R33ST7BFC9JOA8 .cr-truncated-content, #customer_review-R33ST7BFC9JOA8 .cr-full-content&quot;}"><a data-hook="redirect-see-more" aria-label="Toggle full review text" class="a-link-normal a-nowrap a-text-normal" href="/gp/aw/review/B09H3N5J27/R33ST7BFC9JOA8/ref=cm_cr_dp_mb_rvw_tr?ie=UTF8"><span class="a-size-base cr-read-more">See more</span></a></span></div><div class="a-row a-spacing-small cr-full-content aok-hidden"><span data-hook="review-body" class="review-text-sub-contents">
I recently purchased a pair of New Balance Men's Fresh Foam Arishi V4 Running shoes, and I couldn't be happier with my new kicks. These shoes have truly elevated my running experience to another level.<br><br>First and foremost, the comfort and cushioning provided by the Fresh Foam technology are outstanding. It feels like walking on clouds! The cushioned midsole absorbs impact effectively, providing a gentle landing with each stride. Whether I'm running on pavement or hitting the trails, my feet remain well-supported and pain-free throughout my entire run.<br><br>I am also impressed by the breathability of these shoes. The mesh upper allows ample airflow, preventing my feet from feeling sweaty or overheated, even on longer runs. Additionally, the fit is perfect; the shoes wrap snugly around my feet without feeling constricting.<br><br>Another aspect I love about these New Balance shoes is their versatility. They are not only great for running but also perfect for everyday wear. The sleek and stylish design goes well with various outfits, making them suitable for different occasions.<br><br>Durability is yet another aspect worth mentioning. These shoes are built to last. I have been using them for a few months now, and they still look and feel brand new. The robust construction gives me confidence that they will withstand the test of time.<br><br>In summary, the New Balance Men's Fresh Foam Arishi V4 Running shoes are an absolute delight. From their exceptional comfort and breathability to their versatility, anti slip grip and durability, they tick all the boxes for what I want in a running shoe. I highly recommend these shoes to anyone looking for a superior running experience.
</span></div></span>

</span></div></div></div></div><div id="RPZXSYIFPZ1TU" data-hook="mobley-review-content" class="a-section a-spacing-large aok-relative"><div data-hook="genome-widget" class="a-row"><a href="/gp/profile/amzn1.account.AHZJNVIKWF6EKXJD7H6XMCDO3VHA/ref=cm_cr_dp_mb_gw_tr?ie=UTF8" class="a-profile" data-a-size="small"><div aria-hidden="true" class="a-profile-avatar-wrapper"><div class="a-profile-avatar"><img src="https://images-na.ssl-images-amazon.com/images/G/01/x-locale/common/grey-pixel.gif" class="a-lazy-loaded" data-src="https://images-na.ssl-images-amazon.com/images/S/amazon-avatars-global/default._CR0,0,1024,1024_SX110_.png"><noscript><img src="https://images-na.ssl-images-amazon.com/images/S/amazon-avatars-global/default._CR0,0,1024,1024_SX110_.png"/></noscript></div></div><div class="a-profile-content"><span class="a-profile-name">snow47</span></div></a></div><div id="customer_review-RPZXSYIFPZ1TU" class="a-section celwidget" data-csa-c-id="zgbdfc-awrv9p-y6orzs-utdfa2"><div class="a-row a-spacing-micro a-grid-vertical-align a-grid-center"><i data-hook="review-star-rating" class="a-icon a-icon-star-small a-star-small-5 review-rating aok-align-center"><span class="a-icon-alt">5.0 out of 5 stars</span></i><span class="a-letter-space"></span><span data-hook="msrp-avp-badge-linkless" class="a-size-mini a-color-state a-text-bold">Verified Purchase</span></div><span data-hook="review-title" class="a-size-base review-title-content a-color-base a-text-bold">
<span>Good Value Modern Low End Sneaker</span>
</span><div data-hook="review-by-line" class="a-row a-spacing-none reviewByLine"><span data-hook="review-date" class="a-size-small a-color-tertiary review-date">Reviewed in the United States on March 12, 2024</span></div><div class="a-row a-spacing-mini a-grid-vertical-align a-grid-center"><span data-hook="format-strip-linkless" class="a-size-small a-color-tertiary">Size: 10<i class="a-icon a-icon-text-separator" role="img" aria-label="|"></i>Color: Marine Blue/Hot Marigold</span></div><span class="cr-original-truncatable-content">
<div class="a-row a-spacing-small cr-truncated-content"><span data-hook="review-body" class="review-text-sub-contents">
I got these for casual everyday use in the home office/workspace and running errands. For that, they're perfect. Lightweight, comfy breathable upper, easy on and off, and nice looking visually. I ordered a half size up from normal to be able to wear thick socks and just to...
</span><span class="a-letter-space"></span><span class="a-declarative" data-action="reviews:toggle-class:click" data-csa-c-type="widget" data-csa-c-func-deps="aui-da-reviews:toggle-class:click" data-reviews:toggle-class:click="{&quot;cssClass&quot;:&quot;aok-hidden&quot;,&quot;selector&quot;:&quot;#customer_review-RPZXSYIFPZ1TU .cr-truncated-content, #customer_review-RPZXSYIFPZ1TU .cr-full-content&quot;}"><a data-hook="redirect-see-more" aria-label="Toggle full review text" class="a-link-normal a-nowrap a-text-normal" href="/gp/aw/review/B09H3N5J27/RPZXSYIFPZ1TU/ref=cm_cr_dp_mb_rvw_tr?ie=UTF8"><span class="a-size-base cr-read-more">See more</span></a></span></div><div class="a-row a-spacing-small cr-full-content aok-hidden"><span data-hook="review-body" class="review-text-sub-contents">
I got these for casual everyday use in the home office/workspace and running errands. For that, they're perfect. Lightweight, comfy breathable upper, easy on and off, and nice looking visually. I ordered a half size up from normal to be able to wear thick socks and just to have more room; they seem true-to-size. The fresh foam cushioning is decent--it falls in a rare zone of being neither remarkably bouncy, nor uncomfortably firm. I'd spend more for a true running shoe, myself, but these work fine for regular daily activities. They certainly are modern shoes, not just cool-looking retro sneakers that have nothing to cushion your step (I returned a shoe of the latter type before ordering these). All-in-all, feels like good value for something in the $50-$60 range, you get what you pay for.
</span></div></span>

</span></div></div></div></div><div id="R30JLA146AHLLF" data-hook="mobley-review-content" class="a-section a-spacing-large aok-relative"><div data-hook="genome-widget" class="a-row"><a href="/gp/profile/amzn1.account.AHBBBD5P26IM3S3AO5ZEB4UKYTXQ/ref=cm_cr_dp_mb_gw_tr?ie=UTF8" class="a-profile" data-a-size="small"><div aria-hidden="true" class="a-profile-avatar-wrapper"><div class="a-profile-avatar"><img src="https://images-na.ssl-images-amazon.com/images/G/01/x-locale/common/grey-pixel.gif" class="a-lazy-loaded" data-src="https://images-na.ssl-images-amazon.com/images/S/amazon-avatars-global/default._CR0,0,1024,1024_SX110_.png"><noscript><img src="https://images-na.ssl-images-amazon.com/images/S/amazon-avatars-global/default._CR0,0,1024,1024_SX110_.png"/></noscript></div></div><div class="a-profile-content"><span class="a-profile-name">CB</span></div></a></div><div id="customer_review-R30JLA146AHLLF" class="a-section celwidget" data-csa-c-id="cmp9l-v69ou1-qa7zd-uhf327"><div class="a-row a-spacing-micro a-grid-vertical-align a-grid-center"><i data-hook="review-star-rating" class="a-icon a-icon-star-small a-star-small-5 review-rating aok-align-center"><span class="a-icon-alt">5.0 out of 5 stars</span></i><span class="a-letter-space"></span><span data-hook="msrp-avp-badge-linkless" class="a-size-mini a-color-state a-text-bold">Verified Purchase</span></div><span data-hook="review-title" class="a-size-base review-title-content a-color-base a-text-bold">
<span>Finally, a true wide shoe</span>
</span><div data-hook="review-by-line" class="a-row a-spacing-none reviewByLine"><span data-hook="review-date" class="a-size-small a-color-tertiary review-date">Reviewed in the United States on May 23, 2024</span></div><div class="a-row a-spacing-mini a-grid-vertical-align a-grid-center"><span data-hook="format-strip-linkless" class="a-size-small a-color-tertiary">Size: 8.5 Wide<i class="a-icon a-icon-text-separator" role="img" aria-label="|"></i>Color: Nb Navy/Vintage Indigo/Angora</span></div><span class="cr-original-truncatable-content">
<div class="a-row a-spacing-small cr-truncated-content"><span data-hook="review-body" class="review-text-sub-contents">
I finally found a shoe wide enough for both my feet and the prescriptions orthotics. I normally wear a woman’s 9 1/2wide; these are men’s 8 1/2 wide. They felt great a super supportive from the first time I put them on. I also like that they are not some crazy color. The...
</span><span class="a-letter-space"></span><span class="a-declarative" data-action="reviews:toggle-class:click" data-csa-c-type="widget" data-csa-c-func-deps="aui-da-reviews:toggle-class:click" data-reviews:toggle-class:click="{&quot;cssClass&quot;:&quot;aok-hidden&quot;,&quot;selector&quot;:&quot;#customer_review-R30JLA146AHLLF .cr-truncated-content, #customer_review-R30JLA146AHLLF .cr-full-content&quot;}"><a data-hook="redirect-see-more" aria-label="Toggle full review text" class="a-link-normal a-nowrap a-text-normal" href="/gp/aw/review/B09H3N5J27/R30JLA146AHLLF/ref=cm_cr_dp_mb_rvw_tr?ie=UTF8"><span class="a-size-base cr-read-more">See more</span></a></span></div><div class="a-row a-spacing-small cr-full-content aok-hidden"><span data-hook="review-body" class="review-text-sub-contents">
I finally found a shoe wide enough for both my feet and the prescriptions orthotics. I normally wear a woman’s 9 1/2wide; these are men’s  8 1/2 wide. They felt great a super supportive from the first time I put them on. I also like that they are not some crazy color. The soles are hard to keep white, but that’s not an issue for me. The price point was very affordable .

<span>Could be better</span>
</span><div data-hook="review-by-line" class="a-row a-spacing-none reviewByLine"><span data-hook="review-date" class="a-size-small a-color-tertiary review-date">Reviewed in the United States on May 24, 2024</span></div><div class="a-row a-spacing-mini a-grid-vertical-align a-grid-center"><span data-hook="format-strip-linkless" class="a-size-small a-color-tertiary">Size: 8.5 X-Wide<i class="a-icon a-icon-text-separator" role="img" aria-label="|"></i>Color: Black/Black Metallic/Black</span></div><span class="cr-original-truncatable-content">
<div class="a-row a-spacing-small cr-full-content"><span data-hook="review-body" class="review-text-sub-contents">
Feels great when first on. Good for wide feet. No support for ankle. Wouldn’t recommend for long walks or standing. But a quick go to would be ok,for short distance or standing. Little too pricey for what it is. Fits true to size
</span></div></span>

<span>Comfortable</span>
</span><div data-hook="review-by-line" class="a-row a-spacing-none reviewByLine"><span data-hook="review-date" class="a-size-small a-color-tertiary review-date">Reviewed in the United States on May 14, 2024</span></div><div class="a-row a-spacing-mini a-grid-vertical-align a-grid-center"><span data-hook="format-strip-linkless" class="a-size-small a-color-tertiary">Size: 9<i class="a-icon a-icon-text-separator" role="img" aria-label="|"></i>Color: Black/Black Metallic/Black</span></div><span class="cr-original-truncatable-content">
<div class="a-row a-spacing-small cr-truncated-content"><span data-hook="review-body" class="review-text-sub-contents">

</span><span class="a-letter-space"></span><span class="a-declarative" data-action="reviews:toggle-class:click" data-csa-c-type="widget" data-csa-c-func-deps="aui-da-reviews:toggle-class:click" data-reviews:toggle-class:click="{&quot;cssClass&quot;:&quot;aok-hidden&quot;,&quot;selector&quot;:&quot;#customer_review-R3RX9JSFUT846F .cr-truncated-content, #customer_review-R3RX9JSFUT846F .cr-full-content&quot;}"><a data-hook="redirect-see-more" aria-label="Toggle full review text" class="a-link-normal a-nowrap a-text-normal" href="/gp/aw/review/B09H3N5J27/R3RX9JSFUT846F/ref=cm_cr_dp_mb_rvw_tr?ie=UTF8"><span class="a-size-base cr-read-more">See more</span></a></span></div><div class="a-row a-spacing-small cr-full-content aok-hidden"><span data-hook="review-body" class="review-text-sub-contents">
I’ve been having trouble finding a comfortable shoe and I’m so glad I found these. It does feel a little weird at first but after a little bit they broke in. Great support and stability, I had enough room in the toe box which made them so comfortable to wear on my long walks.

<script>
var lopList = "[fr-CA]";
var isAutoTranslateToFrench = false;
var languageOfPreference = "en-US";
if(isAutoTranslateToFrench) {
// auto translation will be enabled based on cookie value. For 1 or undefined we auto translate and for others we show original
// for more details refer: https://w.amazon.com/bin/view/NARX/Projects/FRCX-Customer-Reviews/
var stickyCookieValue = document.cookie.match(/(?:(?:^|.*;\s*)cm-cr-sticky-translate\s*\=\s*([^;]*).*$)|^.*$/).pop();
// Cookie value will be 1 when reviews are translated So checking if reviews are already translated on page load
if (isLoPToAutoTranslateAvailable() && (stickyCookieValue === undefined || stickyCookieValue === "1")) {
P.when('jQuery', 'ready', 'cr-generic-declarative-actions').execute(function ($) {
$('#cr-translate-global').click();
});
}
}
function isLoPToAutoTranslateAvailable() {
for(const lop of lopList.replace('[', '').replace(']', '').split(',')) {
if(lop.trim() === languageOfPreference) {
return true;
}
}
return false;
}
</script>

</span><div class="a-section"><div class="a-box a-box-normal a-color-offset-background a-text-left"><div class="a-box-inner a-padding-medium"><h4 class="a-spacing-mini">How customer reviews and ratings work</h4><p class="a-spacing-mini">Customer Reviews, including Product Star Ratings help customers to learn more about the product and decide whether it is the right product for them.<span class="a-letter-space"></span><a class="a-link-normal" target="_blank" rel="noopener" href="/gp/help/customer/display.html/ref=cm_cr_dp_mb_omni_lm_btn?nodeId=G8UYX7LALQC8V9KA">Learn more how customers reviews work on Amazon</a></p></div></div></div></div>

    for(i = 0 ; i < performance.getEntries().length ; i++){
        var name = performance.getEntries()[i].name ;
        var res = name.match(/\.css\?AUIClients\/AmazonUI/g);
        var initiatorType = performance.getEntries()[i].initiatorType;        

        if(res && initiatorType && initiatorType == "link"){
            var duration = performance.getEntries()[i].duration ;
            ue.count("aui.duration", duration); 
            ue.count("aui.startTime", performance.getEntries()[i].startTime);
            if(duration < 50){ csmTag = "auiCached";}
            else{ csmTag = "auiNotCached";}

            if(window.ue && ue.tag) { ue.tag(csmTag);}
            break;

    }

    P.when('load').execute("log-dpjs-resource-timing", function(){

      function logCSSResourceTiming(metaAssetName, dpEntry) {
        ue.count("dpcssma.duration:" + metaAssetName, dpEntry.duration);
        if(dpmaDuration < 50) {
          ue.tag("dpcssmaCached:" + metaAssetName);
        } else {
          ue.tag("dpcssmaNotCached:" + metaAssetName);
        }
        ue.count("dpcssma.startTime:" + metaAssetName, dpEntry.startTime);
      }

      function logJSResourceTiming(metaAssetName, dpJSEntry) {
        ue.count("dpjsma.duration:" + metaAssetName, dpJSEntry.duration);
        if(dpmaDuration < 50) {
          ue.tag("dpjsmaCached:" + metaAssetName);
        } else {
          ue.tag("dpjsmaNotCached:" + metaAssetName);
        }
        ue.count("dpjsma.startTime:" + metaAssetName, dpJSEntry.startTime);
      }


      var dpEntries = performance.getEntries();
      if(metaAssetNames.length > 0)  {
        for(assetIndex = 0; assetIndex < metaAssetNames.length; assetIndex ++) {
          var metaAssetName = metaAssetNames[assetIndex];
          var cssRE = new RegExp("\\.css\\?AUIClients/" + metaAssetName); 
          var jsRE = new RegExp("\\.js\\?AUIClients/" + metaAssetName); 
          var jsMatched = 0, cssMatched = 0;
          
          for(i = 0 ; i < dpEntries.length; i++) {
            var dpEntry  = dpEntries[i];
            var dpmaDuration = dpEntry.duration;
            var jsRes = dpEntry.name.match(jsRE);
            var cssRes = dpEntry.name.match(cssRE);

            if(!cssMatched && cssRes && dpEntry.initiatorType && dpEntry.initiatorType == "link") {
                logCSSResourceTiming(metaAssetName, dpEntry);
                cssMatched = 1;
            }

            if (!jsMatched && jsRes && dpEntry.initiatorType && dpEntry.initiatorType == "script") {
                logJSResourceTiming(metaAssetName, dpEntry);
                jsMatched = 1;
            }

            if(cssMatched && jsMatched) {
                break;
            }
          }
        }
      }

      for(i = 0 ; i < dpEntries.length ; i++){
          var entry = dpEntries[i];     
          var name = entry.name ;
          var AUIAssetsMatched = false;
          var jQueryAssetsMatched = false;
          var csmTag = "";
          var res = name.match(/\.js\?AUIClients\/AmazonUI/g);  
          var jQRes = name.match(/\.js\?AUIClients\/AmazonUIjQuery/g);  

          if(entry.initiatorType && entry.initiatorType == "script"){

              if(jQRes){
                  ue.count("aui.jQuery.duration", entry.duration); 
                  ue.count("aui.jQuery.startTime", entry.startTime);
                  if(entry.duration < 50) { 
                      csmTag = "auijQueryCached";
                  } else { 
                      csmTag = "auijQueryNotCached";
                  }

                  jQueryAssetsMatched = true;
                  if(window.ue && ue.tag) { ue.tag(csmTag);}            
              } 
              else if(res){
                  ue.count("aui.js.duration", entry.duration); 
                  ue.count("aui.js.startTime", entry.startTime);
                  if(entry.duration < 50) { 
                      csmTag = "auiJSCached";
                  } else { 
                      csmTag = "auiJSNotCached";
                  }

                  AUIAssetsMatched = true;
                  if(window.ue && ue.tag) { ue.tag(csmTag);}            
              } 

              if(AUIAssetsMatched && jQueryAssetsMatched){
                  break;
              }
          }
      }

    });
}
</script>
